    "description": "For Class III VAD devices at MRL 5, absolute hemolysis index predictions shall be verified by experimental-validation against physical bench-top or in-vitro hemolysis measurements. Computational cross-checks are permitted as supplementary evidence only and do not satisfy this requirement independently.",
